{"word":"προηγέομαι","slug":"προηγέομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προηγέομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσομαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to go first and lead the way, to be the leader</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>τινι</el> <i>for</i> a person, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <i>to guide</i> him, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <el>πρ. τὴν ὁδόν</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>to take the lead of</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>;—later, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b>of things, <i>to go before, precede</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>4. </b><a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <el>προηγούμενος, η, ον</el>, <i>going first</i>, <el>τὸ πρ. στράτευμα</el> <i>the van</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}